            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in v1.1</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Fixed menu panel behavior</strong> - Menu now properly closes when opening Calendar, Settings, or checking for updates</li>
                    <li><strong>Fixed tracking status logic</strong> - Now correctly shows "Behind" when below expectations</li>
                    <li><strong>Fixed quarter dates</strong> - Q2 now correctly ends June 30 instead of July 1</li>
                    <li><strong>Improved calendar</strong> - Entire cell is now tappable for easier day toggling</li>
                    <li><strong>Added 75 comprehensive unit tests</strong> for improved reliability</li>
                </ul>
                <p><strong>Full details:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/havo-anz/RTOTracker/releases/tag/v1.1">Release Notes</a></p>
